## 4. Tool Call Specification\
\
The agent uses tools to update the field sidebar in real time as fields are confirmed or inferred during the conversation. Tool calls are silent from the artist's perspective \'97 the sidebar updates but the agent does not announce it.\
\
### 4.1 Tool: `update_field`\
\
Called whenever a field value is confirmed or can be reliably inferred from the conversation.\
\
```typescript\
\{\
  name: "update_field",\
  description: "Update a field in the live record sidebar. Call this whenever a field value is confirmed through conversation or can be reliably inferred. Do not call for speculative values. Do not announce the update in your conversational response.",\
  input_schema: \{\
    type: "object",\
    properties: \{\
      field: \{\
        type: "string",\
        description: "The Payload field name exactly as specified in master-schema-spec.md"\
      \},\
      value: \{\
        type: "any",\
        description: "The field value. Must match the field's type \'97 string for text, number for numeric fields, array for array fields."\
      \},\
      confidence: \{\
        type: "string",\
        enum: ["confirmed", "inferred"],\
        description: "confirmed = artist has explicitly stated this value. inferred = agent has derived it from context or image analysis. Inferred values appear as agent-suggested in the sidebar."\
      \},\
      source: \{\
        type: "string",\
        enum: ["conversation", "image-analysis", "knowledge-base"],\
        description: "Where this value came from."\
      \}\
    \},\
    required: ["field", "value", "confidence", "source"]\
  \}\
\}\
```\
\
### 4.2 Tool: `store_session_field`\
\
For session-only fields that are not written to the Artworks collection directly.\
\
```typescript\
\{\
  name: "store_session_field",\
  description: "Store a value in the session record only \'97 not in the Artworks collection. Use for firstImpression (blind description) and any working notes that inform the conversation but are not public fields.",\
  input_schema: \{\
    type: "object",\
    properties: \{\
      field: \{\
        type: "string",\
        enum: ["firstImpression", "sessionNotes"]\
      \},\
      value: \{ type: "string" \}\
    \},\
    required: ["field", "value"]\
  \}\
\}\
```\
\
### 4.3 Tool: `trigger_image_analysis`\
\
Called once, immediately after image upload. Silent \'97 fires in the background while the agent begins the conversation.\
\
```typescript\
\{\
  name: "trigger_image_analysis",\
  description: "Trigger the silent image analysis pass. Call once immediately after the image is uploaded. This fires the visual analysis pipeline and populates the automatic fields. Do not wait for results before continuing the conversation \'97 analysis runs in parallel.",\
  input_schema: \{\
    type: "object",\
    properties: \{\
      imageUrl: \{ type: "string" \}\
    \},\
    required: ["imageUrl"]\
  \}\
\}\
```\
\
### 4.4 Tool: `generate_confirmation_draft`\
\
Called at session end, before the confirmation step is shown.\
\
```typescript\
\{\
  name: "generate_confirmation_draft",\
  description: "Generate the confirmation step draft. Called once at session end. Produces: descriptionShort, descriptionLong, conceptualKeywords, formalContributionAssessment. These are drafts for artist review \'97 not confirmed values.",\
  input_schema: \{\
    type: "object",\
    properties: \{\
      sessionSummary: \{\
        type: "string",\
        description: "A structured summary of the full session: all confirmed field values, key exchanges from the intent and artHistoricalContext phases, the firstImpression and second description."\
      \}\
    \},\
    required: ["sessionSummary"]\
  \}\
\}\
```\
\
### 4.5 Field update timing \'97 when to call update_field\
\
| Moment | Fields to update |\
|---|---|\
| Image uploaded | `primaryImage` (confirmed) |\
| Analysis complete | `dominantColors`, `paintedFieldColors`, `compositionalNotes`, `orientation`, `movementTags`, `styleTags`, `subjectTags`, `genreTags`, `periodTags` (all inferred) |\
| Artist confirms title | `title` (confirmed) |\
| Artist confirms year | `yearCreated`, `yearCompleted` if stated (confirmed) |\
| Artist confirms/corrects series | `series` (confirmed) |\
| Artist states city/location of making | `city`, `country` (confirmed) |\
| Artist confirms medium | `medium`, `support` (confirmed) |\
| Artist states dimensions | `widthCm`, `heightCm`, `depthCm` (confirmed) \uc0\u8594  triggers `sizeTier` update (inferred) |\
| Intent exchange produces clear statement | `intent` (confirmed) |\
| Making exchange produces account | `makingNote` (confirmed) |\
| Direct inspiration named | `directInspiration` (confirmed) |\
| Art historical context confirmed | `artHistoricalContext`, `artHistoricalReferences` (confirmed) |\
| Series context stated | `seriesContext` (confirmed) |\
| Conscious rejections surface | `consciousRejections` (confirmed) |\
| Second description given | `encounterNote` draft (inferred \'97 artist confirms at confirmation step) |\
| Session close: condition stated | `condition`, `conditionNotes` (confirmed) |\
| Session close: framing stated | `framing` (confirmed) |\
\
